edented in the annals of our club. I appreciate Edo State Deputy Governor, His Excellency, Rt. Hon. Philip Shaibu who graced and played the tournament along with others too. Vanguard News Nigeria The course of Ibori Golf and Country Club (IGCC), in Asaba, Delta State capital, will come alive this morning as the Captain’s inaugural tournament tees off. The tournament earlier scheduled for the second quarter of this year was postponed due to Coronavirus pandemic and its consequent effect on activities worldwide.… November 23, 2020 In "Sports" Angela Uwabor of Ibori Golf and Country Club (IGCC), Asaba has won the Ladies best Net at the maiden Delta Open Golf Tournament which ended on Sunday July 30, 2013 In "Sports" As you read this piece, Sapele Athletic Club Golf section is a beehive of activities. The 18 holes golf facility which is arguably the oldest in the country, recently converted some of its browns to greens and its playing host to over 100 male and female golfers taking part in… February 5, 2010 In "Sports"